535
00:38:22,378 --> 00:38:26,632
- That's all.
- We were only trying to drown her.

536
00:38:26,716 --> 00:38:29,635
- Ya see?
- Well, if you think for one minute...

537
00:38:29,719 --> 00:38:32,930
- that I'm going to put up with a...
- Shh. Hold it, Wendy.

538
00:38:38,478 --> 00:38:42,482
- Yep, it's Hook, all right.
- Hook!
- Hook!

539
00:38:42,565 --> 00:38:44,525
Hook! Oh!

540
00:38:44,609 --> 00:38:47,403
Quick, Wendy.

541
00:38:49,739 --> 00:38:52,408
They've captured Tiger Lily.

542
