- Mr Smee!

576
00:41:46,541 --> 00:41:49,752
Just exactly what do you
think you are doing?

577
00:41:49,836 --> 00:41:52,380
Putting her back
like you said, Captain.

578
00:41:52,463 --> 00:41:54,674
